%N A394978 Expansion of -1/(Sum_{k>=0} binomial(3*k+1,k) * x^k).
%F A394978 G.f.: -1/B(x) where B(x) is the g.f. of A045721.
%F A394978 G.f.: (2*g-3)/g^2 where g = 1+x*g^3 is the g.f. of A001764.
%F A394978 a(n) = (1/n) * (4*binomial(3*n-3,n-1) - 2*binomial(3*n-3,n-2)) for n > 0.
